This is a simple and intuitive weather website that allows you to search for weather information by city name. Powered by a reliable weather API, our website provides real-time weather updates for any city you wish to explore.

Features
City Search: Easily search for any city worldwide to get the latest weather information.
Current Temperature: Displays the current temperature for the selected city.
Humidity: Provides the current humidity level.
Wind Speed: Shows the current wind speed to keep you informed about the weather conditions.

Tech Stack
Frontend: HTML, CSS, JavaScript
Backend: Node.js, Express (optional)
API: OpenWeatherMap API
